          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1676375477225-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1698170413996-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1698170413996-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1698170413996-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1698170413996-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1698170413996-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to soften, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>beef stock mix</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Return the <strong>browned meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>tomato sauce & beef meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1676375526036-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1676375526036-x400.jpg",
