        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>farfalle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>farfalle</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1676375533749-x200.jpg",
