        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>farfalle</strong> topped with the <strong>tomato sauce & beef meatballs</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
